snippet.title: Phoenix 2
snippet.description:
Phoenix 2 is a blistering arcade shoot'em up with jaw-dropping graphics where you battle waves of Invaders in daily new missions.
Choose your ship out of 100 different options, each with their own unique weapon and 2 special abilities.

Available on iOS, Android and Steam (PC)
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/phoenix-2/id1134895689
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.firigames.phoenix2
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2678070/Phoenix_2/
